RS: Replica set: (new pod controller in marker) (RC is not use to much in these days)

Problem with ReplicaSet
	1. During version upgradation, RS delete and create all the pods in one go. (application will not accessible till new pods are running) (give downtime)
  2. No rollback.

Benefit with Deployment
	1. Deployment use rolling update strategy (delete and create pods one by one) (means application will always avalible to user). No downtime.
	2. provide rollback. 
